{"content": "I need to multiply 701 \u00d7 638 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 701\u2089 = 7\u00d79\u00b2 + 0\u00d79\u00b9 + 1\u00d79\u2070 = 7\u00d781 + 0 + 1 = 567 + 0 + 1 = 568\u2081\u2080\n- 638\u2089 = 6\u00d79\u00b2 + 3\u00d79\u00b9 + 8\u00d79\u2070 = 6\u00d781 + 3\u00d79 + 8 = 486 + 27 + 8 = 521\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 568 \u00d7 521 = 296,928\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 296928 \u00f7 9 = 32992 r 0\n- 32992 \u00f7 9 = 3665 r 7\n- 3665 \u00f7 9 = 407 r 2\n- 407 \u00f7 9 = 45 r 2\n- 45 \u00f7 9 = 5 r 0\n- 5 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 5\n\nReading from bottom to top: **502270\u2089**\n\n502270", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 338}